<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>After reading through the Zend Form documentation several times I still encountered problems attempting to disable  'Zend_Form_Element_Radio' from escaping html characters within my radio button data. Would it be possible to add a section detailing how to achieve this? I eventually discovered that calling $element-&gt;setAttrib('escape', false) achieved this but had to resort to debugging to figure this out.</p>

